{"tid":452143,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"曝三星X即將發佈GALAXY X","createTime":"2017-10-30T01:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T02:31:31.000Z","uid":141060,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb01ae7e413d1190e70fdea8afc57b03d7fd7bc","tid":452143,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/095552_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F095552_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg&h=892af8db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道在各大手機廠商里，三星一直和蘋果是死對頭，當初和諾基亞平分天下，諾基亞倒下後，三星原本以為可以一統全球手機廠商的江山，可誰知殺出蘋果這匹黑馬，但是現在依然是 全球銷量第一的品牌，在這之前三星首家推出了曲面屏手機，風靡全球，開啟了新的手機設計理念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=bk10i1/3r5n0000rs6q5q3r0090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dbk10i1%2F3r5n0000rs6q5q3r0090.jpg&h=6beb28e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在前幾年還是曲面屏的天下，自從 小米MIX的出現，打破了這個格局，發佈了全球第一款全面屏手機，作為全球手機廠商的龍頭老大，三星怎麼可會善罷甘休，這次又帶了獨家的新概念手機 ：可摺疊手機。"},{"pid":"2c003f054f12a7537458bf3e1ad03f9bcb3d53e2","tid":452143,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"好過買iphone x"},{"pid":"a27654b641ba8b993c20c241d711dd13844a9b77","tid":452143,"uid":81397,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"鐵閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e984f8ac64c32a91d5bba7456bd4235ada6bb2","tid":452143,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"折一下好啦"},{"pid":"6493b20d95df982cda5d91a09ea7a8577ed0828d","tid":452143,"uid":32066,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"幅